# Keep line endings identical on macOS and Windows checkouts.
#
# Without this, a Windows clone with the default `core.autocrlf=true` lands
# every text file with CRLF, which Prettier (whose `endOfLine` default is `lf`)
# then reports as a style violation in all ~90 files at once — `npm run lint`
# becomes unusable rather than informative.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be touched.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.torrent binary
